                     <origDate when="1772">The colophon states that the Ms. was
                        written in 7264 after the creation of the world (= 1772 A.D.), at the time
                        of King Takla Hāymānot (II; r. 1769-77) and Metropolitan ʾIyosʾab (in tenure
